snippet.topLevelComment.snippet.textDisp: Putting up the religious flag was the worst move and uncalled for..

Sunny Deol and BJP goons doing violence to blame farmers who were protesting in the cold peacefully for 60 days.. Please don't go back on your protests.. U r so close.. Don't fall for their mental manipulation.. Stay strong.. Jai jawan, jai kisan..

We strongly condemns violence and this total incident of redfort. But this only half story. Just take a second and think, farmers were protesting peacefully from about 5 months(3 in punjab and 2 in delhi) do what happened all of sudden that they become so violent? 1st thing 1st, government and police already knew that something is going to happen (check godi media's news of last 3 days). They were worried about some anti-social elements from Pakistan. Is our Indian police force so weak?Police didn't stop protesters when only 20 tractors reached redfort, they were just sitting under the sun(check video from ndtv handle as prove) question is why they waited? Only when 100s of tractors gathered, they used tear gas and lathi march as a result people became violent. These were just 2% of total protesting farmers and they went under leadership of Deep sidhu(bjp supporter). Other 98% farmers were tractor marching peacefully as decided by delhi police. But godi media covered only those 2% farmers. Another thing, Indian flag was not harmed at all. It was above all. Other 2 flags were hoisted but at lower level (which was inturn wrong and i criticise that). But think if government wanted, they could stop them at very initial stage but they didn't in order to defame and discredit the whole movement. Because its very easy for  gov.  to shut down violent movement. Moreover 155 farmers have lost their life protesting peacefully. Who is responsible for their loss even during peaceful protest? They are also humans but this godi media don't leave a single chance to show farmer protest as anti natinalist. Just think about those 98% others and not just these government motivated 2%.  History shows only peaceful protest stay for that long to be won. Best way to disrupt any protest is to invite violence.  Do your research and then conclude . Peace!

snippet.topLevelComment.snippet.textDisp: The inability to understand democratic protest  and the strength of a democratic peaceful protest. This was coming , there was all the premonition that at one point there will be some breakaway and the efforts to control and govern and mitigate a dissent and a solution  peacefully will be lost. The responsibility lies squarely on the Central leadership of BJP. Presently the majority party at the central parliament. And it points very clearly to Mr. Narendra Modi and Mr. Amit Shah, having most of the blood in their hands. The inability to understand the resilient and steadfastness of the farmers demands even after 10 rounds of talks and more then 50 days of peaceful protest around the nation's capital is a tell tale sign of lack of governance of both the BJP politicians and also the Indian administrative machinery. Result: The inevitable mixed state of messaging from both farmer  protestors and the govt. on the Indian Republic day Celebration on 26th January 2021. The debate and arguments now will follow on the symbolism and who was right and who had wronged. But, it remains that the Benevolence of a democratic nation to it's people has not been shown now for many years since independence.  And sadly we call that India . --- Nilotpal Bhattacharyya Jan 26th 2021
